## Test Results

**24 tests passed:**
- Graph creation (directed/undirected)
- Negative weight handling
- Negative cycle detection
- Algorithm correctness verification
- Quantum-inspired reproducibility with seed

---

## Generated Results

Ran comparison on **6 curated graphs**, each with its own folder:

| Graph | Key Finding |
|-------|-------------|
| sparse_basic | All algorithms found same path (distance 10) |
| dense_mesh | Same optimal path across algorithms |
| negative_shortcut | Paths matched despite negative edge |
| bottleneck | Different paths through chokepoint |
| diamond_paths | Tie-breaking behavior tested |
| **negative_cycle** | **Bellman-Ford detected negative cycle** |

